quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  93,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  93,1,qasam hai roz roshan ki
  93,2,aur raat ki jabkay woh sukoon ke sath taari ho jaye
  93,3,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tumahray Rab ne tum ko hargiz nahi chorra aur nah woh naraaz howa
  93,4,aur yaqeenan tumahray liye baad ka daur pehlay daur se behtar hai
  93,5,aur anqareeb tumhara Rab tum ko itna day ga ke tum khush ho jao ge
  93,6,kya is ne tum ko yateem nahi paaya aur phir thikana faraham kya ?
  93,7,aur tumhe nawaqif raah paaya aur phir hadaayat bakhsh
  93,8,aur tumhe nadaar paaya aur phir maldaar kar diya
  93,9,lehaza yateem par sakhti nah karo
  93,10,aur sa-il ko nah jhirko
  93,11,aur apne Rab ki Nemat ka izhaar karo
